name: The Birth of Emotion
description:
The evolution of humanity rising from durable and resilient, microscopic life forms into giant sentient sugar cubes, who are emotionally inept and roaming around Earth searching for happiness and satisfaction but eventually just die, miserable and alone. 

Meh.
